steps.name: I click in the new post button with selector "a[data-test-new-post-button]"
I enter title "$name_postTitle" into field with selector "textarea[data-test-editor-title-input]"
I click in the Publish button
I click in the Right now button
I click in the shedule later button with selector "div.gh-radio"
I click in the Continue, final review button with selector "button[data-test-button='continue']"
I click in the Publish post confirm button with selector "button[data-test-button='confirm-publish']"

I go back to the list of posts clicking the posts button with selector "a[data-test-link='posts']"
I validate that the post was sheduled successfully
